5:["$","div",null,{"className":"flex min-h-screen flex-col","children":[["$","$Le",null,{}],["$","main",null,{"className":"flex-1","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"container max-w-4xl py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"text-center space-y-4","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"font-headline text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl","children":"The 90-Day Executive Sale Plan: How to Sell Your Oakville Home Fast & For Top Dollar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"August 28, 2025"}]]}],["$","$Lf",null,{"className":"my-8"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert","children":[["$","p","p-0",{"children":"Selling an executive home in Oakville on a tight timeline presents a unique challenge. Whether driven by a corporate relocation, a new business venture, or a personal opportunity, the goal is clear: a swift, seamless transaction that maximizes your significant investment. A standard selling approach won't suffice."}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":"This is your 90-day action plan, designed for the discerning Oakville homeowner who values time, efficiency, and results."}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":["$","img","img-0",{"src":"/90-day-sale-plan-body.jpg","alt":"90-Day Executive Sale Plan"}]}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-0",{"children":"Phase 1: The First 72 Hours – Immediate Strategic Decisions"}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"The clock is ticking. Decisive action in the first three days is critical to setting up a successful sale."}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"className":"contains-task-list","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Engage a Local Market Expert:"}]," Your first call should be to a real estate professional who specializes in Oakville's luxury market and has a proven track record with accelerated sales. They will act as your project manager for the entire process."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Establish a Pricing Strategy:"}]," In a time-sensitive sale, pricing is a strategic tool, not an aspiration. Your agent will provide a data-driven analysis to price your home competitively for the current market, attracting immediate attention from serious, qualified buyers."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Sign the Listing Agreement:"}]," This authorizes your agent to begin executing the marketing plan immediately."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":["$L10"," ","$L11"," Notify your lawyer of your timeline so they can prepare to handle the transaction with the required speed."]}],"\n"]}],"\n","$L12","\n","$L13","\n","$L14","\n","$L15","\n","$L16","\n","$L17","\n","$L18","\n","$L19","\n","$L1a","\n","$L1b","\n","$L1c"]}],"$L1d","$L1e"]}]}],"$L1f","$L20"]}]
