14:["$","ul","ul-1",{"className":"contains-task-list","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Schedule the \"Power Team\" Walk-Through:"}]," Your agent should immediately bring in their professional home stager and photographer for a single, comprehensive consultation. You will leave with a clear, prioritized list of actions."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Deploy Professional Services:"}]," Do not spend your own valuable time on deep cleaning or decluttering.\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"$undefined","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Executive Decluttering Service:"}]," Hire a service to pack non-essential items and move them to a secure, off-site storage unit."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"$undefined","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Professional Deep Clean:"}]," A team will clean the entire home, including windows, carpets, and appliances, to a showroom standard."]}],"\n"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Conduct a Pre-Listing Inspection:"}]," This is non-negotiable for an accelerated sale. By identifying and addressing any potential issues upfront, you eliminate objections, build buyer confidence, and remove the possibility of a deal falling apart over a surprise inspection report. This move signals to the market that your home is a premium, transparent offering."]}],"\n"]}]
